conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It has an official CMF number - Promotes specific party achievements - Links current presidential candidate (Ciolacu) to positive achievements - Is paid advertising targeting a large audience - Uses party branding and messaging
